      <title>石油交易商在市场紧张的情况下权衡伊朗和以色列冲突的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/oil-prices-iran-israel-conflict-adds-risks-in-tight-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗和以色列之间不断升级的冲突将迫使石油交易商重新评估他们所需的地缘政治风险溢价，以应对供需基本面紧张已推动油价突破每桶90美元的市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/oil-prices-iran-israel-conflict-adds-risks-in-tight-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 13:48:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币“减半”将对加密货币矿工造成 100 亿美元的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/bitcoin-halving-will-deal-a-10-billion-blow-to-crypto-miners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于比特币的爱好者来说，每四年一次的软件更新（称为“减半”）长期以来一直被视为支撑其价值的关键之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/bitcoin-halving-will-deal-a-10-billion-blow-to-crypto-miners</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
