      <title>伊朗袭击以色列后市场评估报复周期的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/markets-weigh-up-risk-of-retaliation-cycle-as-iran-hits-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新的一周，金融市场将面临地缘政治的担忧，这在很大程度上取决于伊朗周末对以色列前所未有的袭击是否会引发多轮报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/markets-weigh-up-risk-of-retaliation-cycle-as-iran-hits-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 12:16:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元碾压同行，新兴市场与弱势货币作斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/emerging-markets-battle-weak-currencies-as-dollar-crushes-peers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[货币干预已成为新兴市场尤其是亚洲的一个关键战场，因为美元的最新上涨给官员们带来了采取行动的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/emerging-markets-battle-weak-currencies-as-dollar-crushes-peers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将保持关键利率和流动性稳定以巩固复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/china-set-to-keep-key-rate-liquidity-steady-to-cement-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，当政策性贷款到期时，中国可能会维持关键利率并保持流动性充裕，从而维持宽松的条件，以帮助不完整的经济复苏和增加债务销售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/china-set-to-keep-key-rate-liquidity-steady-to-cement-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪政党在选举宣言中誓言增长、发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/modi-s-party-targets-growth-development-in-election-manifesto-luz36d3m</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪在本周的投票中争取历史性的第三个任期，印度执政党在其选举宣言中承诺将重点放在基础设施上，并保留民众补贴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-14/modi-s-party-targets-growth-development-in-election-manifesto-luz36d3m</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Apr 2024 04:48:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肖尔茨抵达中国，旨在缓和紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/scholz-heads-to-china-on-a-mission-to-dial-down-trade-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨本周将向中国传达一个微妙的信息：北京尚未按照欧洲警告采取行动，终止歧视性商业行为，否则将导致紧张局势升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/scholz-heads-to-china-on-a-mission-to-dial-down-trade-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗袭击导致比特币暴跌给全球市场发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/bitcoin-btc-steadies-after-sinking-most-since-2023-on-iran-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币在经历了一年多以来的最大跌幅后，一直在努力争取牵引力，这是由于中东地缘政治紧张局势升级引发避险情绪而导致加密货币市场大范围下跌的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/bitcoin-btc-steadies-after-sinking-most-since-2023-on-iran-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 22:57:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界经济的大逃亡并没有给二十国集团带来安慰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/world-economy-s-great-escape-is-no-comfort-to-the-g-20</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果世界经济正在走向软着陆，那么一路上将会有很多焦虑，伊朗对以色列的导弹袭击给全球带来了不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/world-economy-s-great-escape-is-no-comfort-to-the-g-20</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗革命卫队在霍尔木兹海峡附近扣押集装箱船</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-13/urgent-british-military-warns-of-possible-vessel-being-boarded-near-strait-of-hormuz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[耶路撒冷（美联社）——周日早些时候，伊朗发射了数百架无人机、弹道导弹和巡航导弹，执行前所未有的报复任务，将中东推向一场地区性战争，随后以色列各地响起了隆隆声和空袭警报。一名军方发言人表示，发射次数超过 300 次，但其中 99% 被拦截。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-13/urgent-british-military-warns-of-possible-vessel-being-boarded-near-strait-of-hormuz</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 08:20:12 GMT</pubDate>
